{NORTH has a rotten hand, and many players would just pass 1NT.

But NORTH figures that having SOUTH play any 4-4 fit would be better than 1NT so 
he bids 2\C, Stayman. This is called "Garbage Stayman", and you can see why.

SOUTH bids 2\H and NORTH passes. He would have passed 
either 2\S or 2\D also.}

